{n \choose h}{n-k \choose k} \\ = \frac{n!}{h!(n-h)!}\frac{(n-h)!}{k!(n-h-k)!} \\ = \frac{n!}{h!k!(n-h-k)!} \\ =\frac{n!}{k!(n-k)!}\frac{(n-k)!}{h!(n-h-k)!} \\ ={n\choose k}{n-k\choose h}
